column1: Observed Geomagnetic Storm Parameters:Max Kp: 4.0Dst min. in nT: -23 Dst min. time: 2017-09-07T09:00Z  CME Note: Associated with M5.5 flare from AR 12673. CME start time was updated from 2017-09-04T23:06Z. Note that there was also a CME starting on 2017-09-04T19:39Z that was slightly slower but in a similar direction and was likely "merged" with the faster 2017-09-04T20:36Z CME.
